DashboardDefinitionComponents.Name: Data Status
DashboardDefinitionComponents.Parameters:
[{"WidgetSubTitle":"","WidgetType":"grid","WidgetFilterField":"","WidgetColor":"","WidgetFrameStyle":{},"WidgetXPosition":0,"WidgetYPosition":2,"WidgetRows":49,"WidgetColumns":47,"WidgetHeader":{"showTitle":true,"showSubTitle":false,"WidgetMetrics":{"visible":false,"Metrics":[]},"WidgetPeriodChooser":{"visible":false,"type":"","startDate":null,"endDate":null}},"WidgetDataSources":{"main":{"type":"querytext","value":"WITH ResetDataLogs AS
(
	SELECT 
		rl.Datamart,
		Year(rl.FromDate) as [Year],
		Month(rl.FromDate) as [Month],
		MIN(rl.FromDate) as DatamartBeginDate,
		MAX(rl.ToDate) as DatamartEndDate,
		MIN(rl.StartedOn) as StartedOn,
		MAX(rl.FinishedOn) as FinishedOn,
		MAX(IIF(rl.FinishedOn is null, 1, 0)) as Updating
	FROM 
		Analytics.ResetLogs rl
	WHERE
		rl.FromDate >= @FromDate AND
		rl.ToDate <= @ToDate
	GROUP BY
		rl.Datamart,
		Year(rl.FromDate),
		Month(rl.FromDate)
)
SELECT	
	v.Datamart,
	v.DatamartDocumentType,
	v.DatamartBeginDate,
	v.DatamartEndDate,
	v.[Year], 
	v.[Month],
	v.[MonthName], 
	v.OperationalCount as OpCnt,
	v.DataWarehouseCount as DwCnt,
	v.MissingDataWarehouseUpdates as MissingDwUpdts,
	v.MissingDataWArehouseCount as MissingDwCnt,
	IIF(rl.Datamart is null, 0, rl.Updating) as Updating
FROM 
	Analytics.DataWarehouseStatus(@FromDate, @ToDate, 30) v
	LEFT OUTER JOIN ResetDataLogs rl ON (rl.Datamart = v.Datamart AND rl.[Year] = v.[Year] AND rl.[Month] = v.[Month])
","mapping":""}},"Filters":{},"QueryConfiguration":{"RequiredFilters":["FromDate","ToDate","UpdatesMissingMinutes"]}}]
